These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, ambient
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, asparagus
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, aquamarine
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the fan of ambient is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | disco   |
| Food         | asparagus | cauliflower |
| Color     | fuchsia | aquamarine    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda
2 different games are played: go, bridge
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, june
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing go is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Beverage          | water     | mirinda |
| Game   | bridge | go  |
| Birthday           | june         | may     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
House: cape-cod, modern
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, amber
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
There 2 different types of food: kale, spinach
1. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
3. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| House    | modern     | cape-cod |
| Color         | amber | turquise    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Food   | kale         | spinach    |

